                    <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1303453</guid>
                    <description>
                        <![CDATA[<p>小米在早前的西班牙巴塞隆那发布会，除了发布小米 15 Ultra 外，耳机方面亦发布了全新的 Buds 5 Pro 及 Buds 5 Pro Wi-Fi，当中最特别就肯定是后者，毕竟它是市场上首款采用 Wi-Fi 连线与手机连结的耳机，理论上可为耳机带来更广频宽，令用家可以用真无线耳机亦可听到高质无损音乐。但事实是否如此？就让试用了一段时间的 Edward 为大家实测一下吧。</p><h2>小米 Buds 5 Pro / Buds 5 Pro Wi-Fi 开箱直击</h2><p>在为大家分享这两款小米全新真无线耳机的表现前，先让 Edward 为大家带来它们的开箱直击吧。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303459" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc01849-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc01849-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc01849.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303460" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc02253-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc02253-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc02253.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲这两款就是小米最新推出的 Buds 5 Pro（上）及 Buds 5 Pro Wi-Fi（下）真无线耳机，现在就让 Edward 为大家开箱。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303461" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc01856-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc01856-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc01856.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303462" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc02255-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc02255-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc02255.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲从盒面大家已可看出两者的分别，Wi-Fi 版盒面会印有 Wi-Fi 一字。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303463" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc01868-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc01868-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc01868.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303464" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc02263-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc02263-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc02263.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲两只耳机一打开盒就已经会见到耳机盒真身，耳机就收藏在充电盒内。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303465" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc01871-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc01871-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc01871.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303466" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc02266-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc02266-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc02266.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲而两只耳机底层均见到说明书，其他配件就收藏在顶部及底部的夹层。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303467" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc01873-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc01873-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc01873.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303468" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc02267-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc02267-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc02267.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲两款耳机均会附送 USB-A to USB-C 充电线，以及另外三个不同大细的耳塞（XS、S 及 L），而已装在耳机的就是 M 码。至此两款耳机开箱已完成。</p><h2>设计小不同但类近</h2><p>今次小米发布的两款全新真无线耳机 Buds 5 Pro（下文简称 B5P）及 Buds 5 Pro Wi-Fi（下文简称 B5P Wi-Fi），其实两者均是属于 Buds 5 系列，所以在设计语言上两只新耳机均颇为相近，唯一较大分别是 B5P Wi-Fi 采用半透明充电盒，而且充电盒内边位两处位置印有红色标记；而 B5P 就采用了镜面设计的充电盒，盒内亦没有相关红色标记而已。这两个位就是分辨是否 Wi-Fi 版本的方法，其他无论是大细、重量、按键 / 插槽位置，两者均是相同的。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303470" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc01882-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc01882-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc01882.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303471" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc02276-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc02276-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc02276.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲小米 Buds 5 Pro（上）及 Buds 5 Pro Wi-Fi（下）毕竟属于同一系列，所以设计十分相近，最明显分别就是充电盒方面，前者采用镜面设计，而后者就采用半透式设计。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303472" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc02279-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc02279-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc02279.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲而打开充电盒，就会见到 Buds 5 Pro Wi-Fi（右）的盒盖及右耳机充电位旁均有一个红色标记，但 Buds 5 Pro（左）的充电盒就没有这个设计。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303474" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc02285-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc02285-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc02285.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲另外，两款耳机机身均采用哑面平实设计。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303473" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc01908-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc01908-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc01908.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲而两款耳机的耳柄均加入了抛光设计，还算有一定的层次感。</p><br /><b>
]]>
                    </description>
